籤詩版本二:
E like me ka swan e lele ana mai ka hīnaʻi, makemake au e kiʻi i kino ʻē aʻe akā ʻaʻole hiki
He paʻakikī ka hele ʻana mai ka ʻākau, hema, hikina a me ke komohana, makaʻu maoli kēia hexagram i ka inaina.
詩意:
Ua like kēia hexagram me ka swan e hoʻolei ana iā ia iho i loko o ka wai (cage).
ʻOi aku ka hakahaka a me ka liʻiliʻi maoli.
解曰: ʻAʻole hiki ke komo i ke kino. To regress is to be (i) hiki. E mālama i kou poʻo i lalo a hele pololei. ʻO nā mea a pau i loko.
籤詩故事一:
◇ Ua lanakila a hoʻopio ʻo Qin i ʻekolu mau luna koa
ʻAʻole i hoʻolohe ʻo Duke Mu o Qin i ka ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo a kāna kuhina kahiko ʻo Jian Gong a hoʻouna aku i nā pūʻali koa e hoʻouka i ka mokuʻāina ʻo Zheng, ua hakakā ʻo ia me ka poʻe o Jin ma Huo (aia ma waena o Luoning County a me Shaanxian County ma Henan Province, Kina).
Ua hoʻowalewale ka pūʻali Jin i ka pūʻali Qin i ke awāwa weliweli, ua ālai ʻia ke alanui ma mua. lehulehu o na poino.
Ua pio lākou a ua pio nā pūkaua ʻekolu.
聖意: ʻAʻole ʻoluʻolu ma ka home, paʻa ʻia, ʻimi kālā, hewa, kālepa, hoʻopau i ka male, hoʻopaʻi, hōʻeha, hoʻopaʻi, powa, keakea hele wāwae, nele i nā enuhe silika, ahulau, nalo nā kānaka, hoʻopiʻi, pōʻino, neʻe, lilo ka waiwai, maʻi ʻino, hohola mauna a me na luakupapau
古人: Ua lanakila ʻo Qin a hoʻopio i nā luna ʻekolu
